#: ../channels/email/index.rst:47 ../channels/email/index.rst:7
msgid ""
"(Self-hosted users may have already completed this step during new system "
"setup.)"
msgstr ""
"(Gli utenti self-hosted potrebbero aver già completato questo passaggio "
