#: ../channels/email/index.rst:54 ../channels/email/index.rst:14
msgid ":doc:`🗂️ Filters <filters>`"
msgstr ":doc:`🗂️ Filtri <filters>`"

#: ../channels/email/index.rst:53 ../channels/email/index.rst:13
msgid ""
"**Make sure new tickets show up in the right place** with automated, if-this-"
"then-that rules for all incoming email."
msgstr ""
"**Assicurati che i nuovi ticket arrivino nel posto giusto** con regole "
"automatizzate del tipo se-questo-allora-quello per tutte le email in arrivo."

#: ../channels/email/index.rst:57 ../channels/email/index.rst:17
