"`WhatsApp Business Platform <https://developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp>`_"
msgstr ""
"`WhatsApp Business Platform <https://developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp>`_"

#: ../channels/whatsapp/preparation.rst:15
