msgstr "📅 Pubblicazione programmata"

#: ../manage/knowledge-base.rst:31
msgid "📎 File attachments"
msgstr "📎 Allegati file"

#: ../manage/knowledge-base.rst:32
msgid ""
"🔗 Wiki-style internal linking to both 💡 **KB answers** and 📋 **tickets**"
msgstr ""
"🔗 Collegamenti interni in stile wiki sia a 💡 **risposte KB** che a 📋 "
"**ticket**"

#: ../manage/knowledge-base.rst:33
msgid "🖼️ Rich text editor + embedded images"
msgstr "🖼️ Editor di testo ricco + immagini incorporate"

#: ../manage/knowledge-base.rst:36 ../manage/slas.rst:21
