"in {} with the domain of your Zammad)"
msgstr ""
"Endpoint: ``https://{tuo.dominio.tld}/api/v1/checklists`` (sostituisci il "
"valore in {} con il dominio del tuo Zammad)"

#: ../manage/webhook/examples/add-checklist-to-ticket.rst:26
