msgstr "Metodo di richiesta: ``POST``"

#: ../manage/webhook/examples/add-checklist-to-ticket.rst:27
msgid "Authentication: **Bearer Token**"
msgstr "Autenticazione: **Bearer Token**"

#: ../manage/webhook/examples/add-checklist-to-ticket.rst:28
msgid "Bearer token: paste the token you created before"
msgstr "Bearer token: incolla il token che hai creato in precedenza"

#: ../manage/webhook/examples/add-checklist-to-ticket.rst:29
msgid ""
"Custom payload: activate it and add the following snippet. Make sure to "
"replace the value ``1`` for ``template_id`` with the ID of your checklist "
"template."
msgstr ""
