"Find your webhook in the list on the management screen and click on it to "
"edit it."
msgstr ""
"Trova il tuo webhook nell'elenco nella schermata di gestione e cliccaci "
"sopra per modificarlo."

#: ../manage/webhook/examples/mattermost-notifications.rst:125
#: ../manage/webhook/examples/microsoft-teams-notifications.rst:139
#: ../manage/webhook/examples/rocket-chat-notifications.rst:121
