"structure."
msgstr ""
"Successivamente, identifica la riga che inizia con il blocco ``\"text\": "
"\"...`` nella struttura JSON."

#: ../manage/webhook/examples/mattermost-notifications.rst:None
msgid "Custom Payload for Mattermost Webhook"
msgstr "Payload Personalizzato per Webhook Mattermost"

#: ../manage/webhook/examples/mattermost-notifications.rst:136
#: ../manage/webhook/examples/rocket-chat-notifications.rst:132
#: ../manage/webhook/examples/slack-notifications.rst:145
msgid ""
"Scroll horizontally to the end of the line and select "
"``\\n\\n#{notification.body}`` part near the end. Be sure not to include the "
"end double quote with comma (``\",``) in the rest of the line, since the new "
