msgstr "Payload Personalizzato con Contenuto Articolo per Webhook Mattermost"

#: ../manage/webhook/examples/mattermost-notifications.rst:146
#: ../manage/webhook/examples/rocket-chat-notifications.rst:142
#: ../manage/webhook/examples/slack-notifications.rst:155
