msgstr "Payload del webhook di Microsoft Teams"

#: ../manage/webhook/examples/microsoft-teams-payload.rst:4
msgid ""
"Microsoft is retiring their Office 365 connectors in favor of connecting "
"third-party tools via their Workflows. Because of that, the pre-defined "
"webhook in Zammad has changed. In case you need the old or new default "
