#: ../manage/webhook/examples/rocket-chat-notifications.rst:59
msgid ""
"In the subsequent modal dialog, select **Rocket Chat Notifications** as the "
"pre-defined webhook."
msgstr ""
"Nella finestra di dialogo modale successiva, seleziona **Notifiche Rocket "
