#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:2
msgid "SAML"
msgstr "SAML"

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:7
msgid ""
"Connect your SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) identity provider as "
"a single sign-on (SSO) method. SAML is an open standard for SSO "
"authentication (among other things). Sign-ins are shared across multiple "
"**service providers** and managed by a central **identity provider** (IdP)."
msgstr ""
"Connetti il tuo identity provider SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) "
"come metodo di single sign-on (SSO). SAML è uno standard aperto per "
"l'autenticazione SSO (tra le altre cose). Gli accessi sono condivisi tra più "
"**service provider** e gestiti da un **identity provider** (IdP) centrale."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:12
msgid ""
"In this case, the service provider is Zammad, and the IdP is a software "
"service that you either host or subscribe to (e.g. `Keycloak <https://"
"www.keycloak.org/>`_, `Redhat SSO Server <https://access.redhat.com/products/"
"red-hat-single-sign-on>`_, `ADFS <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-"
"server/identity/active-directory-federation-services>`_, or `Okta <https://"
"www.okta.com/>`_)."
msgstr ""
"In questo caso, il service provider è Zammad, e l'IdP è un servizio software "
"che ospiti o a cui ti abboni (ad es. `Keycloak <https://www.keycloak.org/"
">`_, `Redhat SSO Server <https://access.redhat.com/products/red-hat-single-"
"sign-on>`_, `ADFS <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-server/identity/"
"active-directory-federation-services>`_, o `Okta <https://www.okta.com/>`_)."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:19
msgid ""
"This guide assumes you are already using SAML within your organization (i.e. "
"that your IdP is fully set up)."
msgstr ""
"Questa guida presuppone che tu stia già utilizzando SAML all'interno della "
"tua organizzazione (cioè che il tuo IdP sia completamente configurato)."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:23
msgid "Basic Configuration"
msgstr "Configurazione di base"

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:25
msgid ""
"This section describes the setup of an IdP in a general way. See :ref:`saml-"
"guides` for setup guides for Keycloak and Microsoft SAML."
msgstr ""
"Questa sezione descrive la configurazione di un IdP in modo generale. "
"Vedi :ref:`saml-guides` per le guide di configurazione per Keycloak e SAML "
"di Microsoft."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:29
msgid "Configure Your IdP"
msgstr "Configura il tuo IdP"

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:32
msgid "Add Zammad as a Client/App"
msgstr "Aggiungi Zammad come Client/App"

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:34
msgid ""
"Import Zammad into your IdP using the XML configuration found at ``https://"
"your.zammad.domain/auth/saml/metadata``."
msgstr ""
"Importa Zammad nel tuo IdP utilizzando la configurazione XML trovata su "
"``https://your.zammad.domain/auth/saml/metadata``."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:37
msgid ""
"If your IdP doesn't support XML import, you will have to configure Zammad as "
"a new client/app manually using the above XML metadata file for reference."
msgstr ""
"Se il tuo IdP non supporta l'importazione XML, dovrai configurare Zammad "
"come un nuovo client/app manualmente utilizzando il file di metadati XML "
"sopra come riferimento."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:40
msgid "For instance, when you see this tag:"
msgstr "Ad esempio, quando vedi questo tag:"

#: ../settings/security/third-party/saml.rst:46
msgid ""
