msgstr ""
"Definisce il backend per le ricerche del calendario geografico. Utilizzato "
"per la configurazione iniziale del calendario."

#: ../settings/system/services.rst:16
msgid "Default: ``Zammad GeoCalendar Service`` (active)"
msgstr "Predefinito: ``Servizio Calendario Geo Zammad`` (attivo)"

#: ../settings/system/services.include.rst:2
msgid ""
"Make sure your on premise installation has ``HTTPS`` access to "
"``geo.zammad.com``."
msgstr ""
"Assicurati che la tua installazione on-premise abbia accesso ``HTTPS`` a "
"``geo.zammad.com``."

#: ../settings/system/services.rst:26
msgid "Geo IP Service"
msgstr "Servizio Geo IP"

#: ../settings/system/services.rst:21
msgid ""
"Defines the backend for geo IP lookups. Shows also location of an IP address "
