msgstr "**Gruppo** *è* ``2nd Level``"

#: ../system/core-workflows/learn-by-example.rst:52
#: ../system/core-workflows/learn-by-example.rst:109
#: ../system/core-workflows/learn-by-example.rst:217
#: ../system/core-workflows/learn-by-example.rst:256
