msgid "Step 4 (optional): Further configurations for Placetel"
msgstr "Passaggio 4 (opzionale): Ulteriori configurazioni per Placetel"

#: ../system/integrations/cti/provider-configurations/placetel.rst:76
msgid ""
"If needed, you can now configure Zammad's Placetel integration in more "
